                 FSS - This will make the file to check be FSSpeech.Lgui

              TITLES - This will make the file to check be Titles.Lgui

 If this argument is not used, or used but not with a valid Type, the file
 to check will be DSentence.Lgui by default.


 RANGE=Number

 Number is the Syllable range, 1 to 1500, which represents the 1500
 sentences you can define - see the `LGUI.Guide'.


 TRANSLATE=TRUE/FALSE

 Use TRANSLATE=TRUE if you want your Language Text translated into Phonetic
